outputs.output_descr:
The Project aims at;

1- Assessment report to  provide an overview of Jeddah environmental situation.
2- Project document including work plan and budget in preparation for the Environmental Master Plan .
3- Production of Jeddah EMP PD

project_descr: Developing an Urban Environment Action Plan for the city of Jeddah promoting Environmental Protection while ensuring the Sustainable Development of the City and the sustainable livelihoods of its men and women.
project_title: Urban Environment Action Plan for Jeddah City
